00:00:42.510 --> 00:00:44.840
It's not quite with us now.

00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:47.720
But I think it will be
with us reasonably soon.

00:00:47.720 --> 00:00:51.120
And this as you can
see is the book.

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:53.580
Here is my dog, Higgs.

00:00:53.580 --> 00:00:55.340
He's modeling the
book there for you

00:00:55.340 --> 00:00:58.160
